    client = ClientFromEnv()

        client=client,
        body=ModelingCmdReq(
            cmd=Line3d(
                from_=Point3d(

                    z=3.14,

                    x=3.14,
                    y=3.14,
                    z=3.14,

            cmd_id=ModelingCmdId("<uuid>"),
            file_id="<string>",
        ),
    )
